  "prompt": "What is the fee structure of Sri Chaitanya Visakhapatnam?",
  "response": "Sri Chaitanya Educational Institutions have different fee structures depending on the course, location, and type of program (such as regular classes, integrated programs, or distance learning). As of my last update, specific fees for Sri Chaitanya in Visakhapatnam could range widely. Here's a general breakdown based on typical programs offered:\n\n1. **Intermediate (11th and 12th grades):**\n   - Science Stream (MPC/BiPC): Approximately \u20b91,50,000 to \u20b92,00,000 per year.\n   - Commerce Stream: Approximately \u20b91,20,000 to \u20b91,80,000 per year.\n\n2. **Integrated Programs (for competitive exams like IIT-JEE, NEET, etc.):**\n   - These can range from \u20b92,50,000 to \u20b93,50,000 per year, depending on the intensity of the program and additional coaching provided.\n\n3. **Degree Courses (like B.Tech, B.Com, etc.):**\n   - Fees can vary significantly, typically ranging from \u20b91,00,000 to \u20b92,50,000 per year.\n\n4. **Coaching for Competitive Exams:**\n   - Standalone coaching programs for exams like IIT-JEE, NEET, etc., might cost between \u20b91,00,000 to \u20b92,00,000 per year.\n\nPlease note that these are approximate figures and can vary. For the most accurate and up-to-date fee structure, it's essential to contact Sri Chaitanya directly or visit their official website. They often have detailed brochures and can provide specific information tailored to your needs.",
